==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Shoplifter
<hw>Shop"lift`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Shop</ets>
+ <ets>lift.</ets> See <er>Lift</er> to steal.]</ety> <def>One who
steals anything in a shop, or takes goods privately from a shop; one
who, under pretense of buying goods, takes occasion to steal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Shoplifting</ent>⟦br⟧
